{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Summer Stories: At&nbsp;Home","content":"<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At home, it was the usual routine.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The heat and the humidity induced inactivity and made me plod through the daily chores. The rooftop was a vent, if the temperature wasÂ bearable.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1190\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/06/12/summer-stories-at-home/clouds-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"4263,2398\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1434043233&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Clouds-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-1190\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=700&#038;h=393\" alt=\"There was a week of high temperature and humidity, and finally, on the 11th of June, God gifted Kolkata with this sky, a storm, and torrential rainfall!\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=700&amp;h=393 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=1397&amp;h=786 1397w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://