elparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/panorama_try-1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=43 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/panorama_try-1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=129 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/panorama_try-1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=220 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">My First Panorama</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_1186\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1186\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/06/12/summer-stories-at-home/sunset_after_rains/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1919,635\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1428257317&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.02&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"sunset_after_rains\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-1186\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg?w=700&#038;h=231\" alt=\"There was once particular day when it rained a bit. The after effect was wonderful. The golden light filled up our apartment as well!\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg?w=698&amp;h=231 698w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg?w=1396&amp;h=462 1396w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg?w=150&amp;h=50 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg?w=450&amp;h=149 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/sunset_after_rains.jpg?w=768&amp;h=254 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">There was once particular day when it rained a bit. The after effect was wonderful. The golden light filled up our apartment as well!</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_1045\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1045\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/03/24/the-road-to-ilambazar/panorama-1-blog/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"5000,1531\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1427020815&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;27&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0003125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Panorama 1 (blog)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-1045\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg?w=700&#038;h=214\" alt=\"At Shantiniketan!\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg?w=700&amp;h=214 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg?w=1398&amp;h=428 1398w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg?w=150&amp;h=46 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg?w=450&amp;h=138 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/panorama-1-blog.jpg?w=768&amp;h=235 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">At Shantiniketan!</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_1185\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1185\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/06/12/summer-stories-at-home/rooftop_panorama_edited/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"7223,1714\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1430675503&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;21&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.008&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"rooftop_panorama_edited\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-1185\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg?w=700&#038;h=167\" alt=\"This is the last one. I'm still waiting for the sky to get filled with clouds, when the sun sets. Hopefully, this will happen after mid-June.\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg?w=700&amp;h=167 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=332 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg?w=150&amp;h=36 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg?w=450&amp;h=107 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/rooftop_panorama_edited.jpg?w=768&amp;h=182 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">This is the last one.<br />I&#8217;m still waiting for the sky to get filled with clouds, when the sun sets. Hopefully, this will happen after mid-June.</figcaption></figure>\n<hr />\n<h1>Rain andÂ à¦à¦¾à¦² à¦¬à§à¦¶à¦¾à¦à§ (<em>kaal boishakhi</em>)</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">I will probably write a separate post on this, but here&#8217;s an introduction. These two elements provided a solution to every problem, whether I was at hostel, or at home.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em>Why?</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Because itÂ cooled the otherwise horrible weather, and refreshed the mind! The rain, combined with the petrichor, and the lightning, and the occasional storms are the elements that help to revitalize the inhabitants of Kolkata.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We got <em>previews,Â </em>on certain days, during the months of April and May.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the month of April, I learnt how to photograph streaks of lightning. Usually, the <em>mighty effect</em> can be brought by combining several pictures, each picture containing one or moreÂ streaks.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">I couldn&#8217;t do that for several reasons, however I did get a bit lucky.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_1189\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1189\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/06/12/summer-stories-at-home/flash-1-of-2-b-w/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2086,1173\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1429643851&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;6&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Flash (1 of 2) (b-w)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-1189 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg?w=700&#038;h=393\" alt=\"lightning flash\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg?w=700&amp;h=393 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg?w=1398&amp;h=786 1398w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/flash-1-of-2-b-w.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong>This</strong> is a single photograph</figcaption></figure>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After my exams ended, the skies did show more clouds, well defined at the time of sunset.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_1192\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1192\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/06/12/summer-stories-at-home/ghostbuilding/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1920,1280\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1433520709&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;140&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ghostbuilding\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-1192\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg?w=700&#038;h=467\" alt=\"Natural and man made structures\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=934 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/ghostbuilding.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Natural and man made structures</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_1190\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1190\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/06/12/summer-stories-at-home/clouds-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"4263,2398\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1434043233&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Clouds-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-1190\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=700&#038;h=393\" alt=\"There was a week of high temperature and humidity, and finally, on the 11th of June, God gifted Kolkata with this sky, a storm, and torrential rainfall!\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=700&amp;h=393 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=1397&amp;h=786 1397w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/06/clouds-2.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">There was a week of high temperature and humidity, and finally, on the 11th of June, God gifted Kolkata with this sky, a storm, and torrential rainfall!</figcaption></figure>\n<hr />\n<h1>Friends</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">They don&#8217;t deserve any special mentioning, because at every instance of time, they make life more valuable.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At hostel, there are certain people with whom I enjoy spending time most. These people have changed me drastically in the past year.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Friends from my school, and thoseÂ from my locality are my companions at home. Visiting their homes, conversing (and laughing, sometimes for no reason), having <em>phuchka,Â </em>cold drinks, chips &#8211; all these, made the time before and after theÂ <em>exam sessionÂ </em>infinitely better.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">P.S. Thank you Agnij for reminding me that &#8220;moist soil&#8217;s scent&#8221; can be reduced to petrichor ð</p>\n\t\t<div id=\"geo-post-1184\" class=\"geo geo-post\" style=\"display: none\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"latitude\">22.583018</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"longitude\">88.413122</span>\n\t\t</div>","date":"2015-06-12T16:30:00.000Z","slug":"summer-stories-at-home","excerpt":"<p>At home, it was the usual routine. The heat and the humidity induced inactivity and made me plod through the daily chores. The rooftop was a vent, if the temperature wasÂ bearable.</p>\n"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Nabhoneel's Parchments","subtitle":"All thing photographed and written down"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"51474003-5bf3-59bc-bbfd-11b3283b6dbd"}}